## Portfolio Project Notice

This project is created for portfolio and educational purposes to demonstrate
professional Salesforce development skills and best practices.

While the code is provided under the MIT License, users are encouraged to:
- Give appropriate credit when using patterns or code from this repository
- Understand the code rather than blindly copying it
- Adapt patterns to their specific use cases
- Respect the intellectual effort invested in creating this portfolio

